thread.title: Abby McKearin adds to Vermont goals record
thread.title_full: Abby McKearin adds to Vermont goals record - WCAX.COM Local Vermont News, Weather and Sports-

author: Kane O'Neill
title: Abby McKearin adds to Vermont goals record
text: PROCTOR, Vt. - Proctor senior Abby McKearin set the Vermont state record for career goals this past Tuesday and returned to her home field on Saturday for the first time since breaking the record. McKearin was recognized prior to the homecoming game, heading into Saturday's match-up with West Rutland with 154 career goals. McKearin would score on a direct kick in the first half, pushing her state record to 155 career goals, as Proctor defeated West Rutland 2-0.
